IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
Port 993
User a.chaichan@icloud.com
PassCmd "pass apple.com/password"
# Pass xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx
SSLType IMAPS
#CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl@1.1/cert.pem
AuthMechs PLAIN

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore icloud-local
Path ~/mail/
Inbox ~/mail/INBOX
Trash Trash

Channel icloud-folders
Far :icloud-remote:
Near :icloud-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *

Group icloud
Channel icloud-folders
